dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.log.proto.DeviceSwitchingProtocolDetails
dataStructure.description:
This association defines the set of SwitchingProtocols that are currently being used on this LogicalDevice. The supportsProtocol aggregation is used to determine if a particular Protocol (not just a SwitchingProtocol) is supported by this LogicalDevice. The particular semantics of this association are defined by the DeviceSwitchingProtocolDetails association class.

This association class is optional
dataStructure.label: DeviceSwitchingProtocolDetails
